00056 class TypeCode
00057 {
00058 public:
00059     enum Codes
00060     {
00061     //  0
00062         Unknown, Dynamic,
00063     // built-in types (2)
00064         Float, Double, Int, Short, Int24, Long, LongLong, Char, Bool,
00065     // atomic types (11)    
00066         AtomicFloat, AtomicDouble, 
00067         AtomicInt, AtomicLong, AtomicLongLong, AtomicPointer, AtomicExtendedPointer, AtomicDynamicPointer,
00068     // variables (19)
00069         FloatVariable, DoubleVariable, 
00070         IntVariable, ShortVariable, Int24Variable, LongVariable, CharVariable, BoolVariable,
00071     // atomic variables (27)
00072         AtomicFloatVariable, AtomicDoubleVariable, AtomicIntVariable, AtomicLongVariable, 
00073         AtomicPointerVariable, AtomicExtendedPointerVariable, AtomicDynamicPointerVariable,
00074     // arrays (34)
00075         FloatArray, DoubleArray, IntArray, ShortArray, Int24Array, LongArray, CharArray, BoolArray,
00076     // other
00077         Text, TextArray,
00078     // channels (44)
00079         FloatChannel, DoubleChannel, IntChannel, ShortChannel, Int24Channel, LongChannel,
00080     // units (50)
00081         FloatUnit, DoubleUnit, IntUnit, ShortUnit, Int24Unit, LongUnit,
00082     // bus (56)
00083         FloatBus, DoubleBus, IntBus, ShortBus, Int24Bus, LongBus, 
00084     // unit arrays (62)
00085         FloatUnits, DoubleUnits, IntUnits, ShortUnits, Int24Units, LongUnits,
00086     // bus arrays (68)
00087         FloatBusses, DoubleBusses, IntBusses, ShortBusses, Int24Busses, LongBusses, 
00088     // breakpoints (74)
00089         FloatBreakpoints, DoubleBreakpoints, IntBreakpoints, ShortBreakpoints, Int24Breakpoints, LongBreakpoints,
00090     // wavetables (80)
00091         FloatWavetable, DoubleWavetable, IntWavetable, ShortWavetable, Int24Wavetable, LongWavetable,
00092     // signals (87)
00093         FloatSignal, DoubleSignal, IntSignal, ShortSignal, Int24Signal, LongSignal,
00094     // arrays
00095         FloatArrayVariable, DoubleArrayVariable, IntArrayVariable, ShortArrayVariable, 
00096         Int24ArrayVariable, LongArrayVariable, CharArrayVariable, BoolArrayVariable,
00097     // other
00098         TextVariable, TextArrayVariable,
00099     // channels
00100         FloatChannelVariable, DoubleChannelVariable, IntChannelVariable, ShortChannelVariable, Int24ChannelVariable, LongChannelVariable,
00101     // units
00102         FloatUnitVariable, DoubleUnitVariable, IntUnitVariable, ShortUnitVariable, Int24UnitVariable, LongUnitVariable,
00103     // bus (56)
00104         FloatBusVariable, DoubleBusVariable, IntBusVariable, ShortBusVariable, Int24BusVariable, LongBusVariable,

00190     static inline plonk::LongLong getPeak (const int code) throw()
00191     {
00192         static const plonk::LongLong peaks[] = {
00193             0, 0, // invalid
00194             1, 1, INT_MAX, SHRT_MAX, PLONK_INT24_MAX, LONG_MAX, LONG_LONG_MAX, CHAR_MAX, 1, // built-ins
00195             1, 1, INT_MAX, LONG_MAX, LONG_LONG_MAX, // atomics
00196         };
00197         
00198         if ((code >= 0) && (code < TypeCode::AtomicLongLong))
00199             return peaks[code];
00200         else 
00201             return peaks[0];
00202     }
00203     
00206     static inline double getEpsilon (const int code) throw()
00207     {
00208         static const double epsilons[] = {
00209             0, 0, // invalid
00210             FLT_MIN, DBL_MIN, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, // built-ins
00211             FLT_MIN, DBL_MIN, 1, 1, 1 // atomics
00212         };
00213         
00214         if ((code >= 0) && (code < TypeCode::AtomicLongLong))
00215             return epsilons[code];
00216         else 
00217             return epsilons[0];
00218     }

00221     static inline bool isUnknown (const int code) throw()           { return (code == TypeCode::Unknown); }
00222     static inline bool isDynamic (const int code) throw()           { return (code == TypeCode::Dynamic); }
00223     
00224     static inline bool isBuiltIn (const int code) throw()           { return (code >= TypeCode::Float) && (code <= TypeCode::Bool) && code != TypeCode::Int24; }
00225     static inline bool isAtomic (const int code) throw()            { return (code >= TypeCode::AtomicFloat) && (code <= TypeCode::AtomicDynamicPointer); }
00226     static inline bool isVariable (const int code) throw()          { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatVariable) && (code <= TypeCode::BoolVariable); }
00227     static inline bool isAtomicVariable (const int code) throw()    { return (code >= TypeCode::AtomicFloatVariable) && (code <= TypeCode::AtomicDynamicPointerVariable); } 
00228     static inline bool isObjectVariable (const int code) throw()    { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatArrayVariable) && (code <= TypeCode::LongSignalVariable); } 
00229     static inline bool isArray (const int code) throw()             { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatArray) && (code <= TypeCode::TextArray); }
00230     static inline bool isChannel (const int code) throw()           { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatChannel) && (code <= TypeCode::LongChannel); }
00231     static inline bool isUnit (const int code) throw()              { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatUnit) && (code <= TypeCode::LongUnit); }
00232     static inline bool isBus (const int code) throw()               { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatBus) && (code <= TypeCode::LongBus); }
00233     static inline bool isUnits (const int code) throw()             { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatUnits) && (code <= TypeCode::LongUnits); }
00234     static inline bool isBusses (const int code) throw()            { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatBusses) && (code <= TypeCode::LongBusses); }
00235     static inline bool isBreakpoints (const int code) throw()       { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatBreakpoints) && (code <= TypeCode::LongBreakpoints); }
00236     static inline bool isWavetable (const int code) throw()         { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatWavetable) && (code <= TypeCode::LongWavetable); }
00237     static inline bool isSignal (const int code) throw()            { return (code >= TypeCode::FloatSignal) && (code <= TypeCode::LongSignal); }
00238     static inline bool isAudioFileReader (const int code) throw()   { return (code == TypeCode::AudioFileReader); }

00242     static inline bool isFloatType (const int code) throw()         
00243     { 
00244         return (TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Float") == 0) || (TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("AtomicFloat") == 0); 
00245     }
00246     
00247     static inline bool isDoubleType (const int code) throw()        
00248     { 
00249         return (TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Double") == 0) || (TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("AtomicDouble") == 0); 
00250     }
00251     
00252     static inline bool isIntType (const int code) throw()           
00253     { 
00254         return ((TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Int") == 0) && (TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Int24") != 0))
00255                 || (TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("AtomicInt") == 0); 
00256     }
00257     
00258     static inline bool isShortType (const int code) throw()         { return TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Short") == 0; }
00259     static inline bool isInt24Type (const int code) throw()         { return TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Int24") == 0; }
00260     
00261     static inline bool isLongType (const int code) throw()          
00262     { 
00263         return ((TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Long") == 0) && (code != TypeCode::LongLong))
00264                 || (TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("AtomicLong") == 0); 
00265     }
00266     
00267     static inline bool isLongLongType (const int code) throw()      { return TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("LongLong") == 0; }
00268     static inline bool isCharType (const int code) throw()          { return TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Char") == 0; }
00269     static inline bool isBoolType (const int code) throw()          { return TypeCode::getName (code).indexOf ("Bool") == 0; }
00270     
00271     static inline bool isFloatOrDoubleType (const int code) throw() { return TypeCode::isFloatType (code) || TypeCode::isDoubleType (code); }
00272     
00273     static inline bool isIntegralType (const int code) throw()
00274     {
00275         return  TypeCode::isIntType (code)   ||
00276                 TypeCode::isShortType (code) ||
00277                 TypeCode::isInt24Type (code) ||
00278                 TypeCode::isLongType (code)  ||
00279                 (code == TypeCode::LongLong) ||
00280                 TypeCode::isCharType (code)  ||
00281                 TypeCode::isBoolType (code);
00282     }
00283 };
